%U A394754 4660590084476380931695,11432631560731408995190184,52485019398306390820166576777,452485829100092806170863720230804
%N A394754 Number of semi-bipartite structures on n unlabeled vertices.
%C A394754 A semi-bipartite structure is a triple (G,U,V) such that G is a simple graph, U and V form a partition of V[G], and U is isolated in G. a(n) counts non-isomorphic triples (G,U,V) on n unlabeled vertices.
%C A394754 Since U and V form a partition, both must be nonempty. When U or V can be empty, the corresponding sequence is A339832.
%F A394754 a(n) = A339832(n) - A000088(n) - 1 for n >= 1.
%e A394754 For n = 3: a(2)=2 with the following two structures: two isolated vertices with one in U and the other in V; and two connected vertices with one in U and the other in V.
%Y A394754 Cf. A339832, A000088.
%K A394754 nonn
%O A394754 0,3
%A A394754 _Piotr Mitosek_, Mar 31 2026
